official_title: Intervening on Women's Health for Rural Young Cancer Survivors
inclusion_criteria:
* Cancer (Stages 0-IV) diagnosis
* Primary language English or Spanish
* Receiving oncology care at rural oncology clinical participating site
* Living in Imperial County, California
Healthy volunteers allowed
Must be FEMALE
Must have minimum age of 15 Years
Must have maximum age of 50 Years
exclusion_criteria: - Women who are pregnant at recruitment
